{"timestamp": "2025-11-29 17:09:46.131257", "event": "llm_end", "text": "Submission completed.\n\nSummary of submission:\n- is_anomaly: true\n- faulty_devices: [\"router_dist_1_1\"]\n- root_cause_name: [\"ospf_area_misconfiguration\"]\n\nRecommended remediation (optional, not submitted):\n- On router_dist_1_1, add the appropriate OSPF network statements (for example: \"network 10.1.1.0/24 area 1\" and the inter-router link network) to advertise the LAN into OSPF, then verify OSPF adjacency, route propagation, and that hosts on 10.1.1.0/24 obtain DHCP leases and reach the server networks.", "generation_info": {"finish_reason": "stop", "logprobs": null}, "invalid_tool_calls": [], "usage_metadata": {"input_tokens": 2564, "output_tokens": 137, "total_tokens": 2701, "input_token_details": {"audio": 0, "cache_read": 0}, "output_token_details": {"audio": 0, "reasoning": 0}}}
